			Company Description 


			Portlogic Systems, Inc. provides and develops telecom solutions and mobile and Internet software. It also provides electronic payments, ticketing and marketing delivery and community communication systems. The company offers mobile marketing applications, kiosk hardware and software products, includ...
		


                Portlogic Systems, Inc. provides and develops telecom solutions and mobile and Internet software. It also provides electronic payments, ticketing and marketing delivery and community communication systems. The company offers mobile marketing applications, kiosk hardware and software products, including m2Bank, m2Market, m2Ticket, m2Kiosk and m2 Workflow. Portlogic Systems was founded on June 22, 2004 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
            




